{"type":"message","id":"211c7f0e","parentId":"e8e6b85f","timestamp":"2026-02-15T13:24:17.547Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-02-15 15:24 GMT+2] FINAL HOT RELOAD TEST, PERSISTENCE AUDIT & RESEARCH.\n\n1.  **Sandbox Hot Reload (`tests/reload_sandbox.py`):**\n    *   Create script: Monitor `docs_archive/MASTER_PROTOCOL.md`.\n    *   *Action:* Run script in background. Modify `min_margin` in protocol.\n    *   *Goal:* Capture detection time (ms).\n    *   *Constraint:* Use `D:\\Dmarket_bot` paths.\n\n2.  **Persistence Audit:**\n    *   *Ed25519:* Check `dmarket_api.py` for `nacl.signing`.\n    *   *Fleet:* Verify `agent_wrapper.py` has logic for [730, 570, 440, 252490].\n    *   *Safety:* Check if `specs/` and `memory/checkpoints/` exist.\n    *   *Flags:* Check `openclaw.json` for `fleet_mode` and `lazy_loading`.\n\n3.  **Deep Research & Improvement:**\n    *   *DMarket:* Identify \"Target Bid\" strategy implementation details (Bulk targets).\n    *   *ClawHub:* Assess `price-predictor` (Time series/LSTM) and `auto-debugger` (Error healing).\n    *   *News:* Compile 1 headline per game (CS2, Dota 2, TF2, Rust).\n\n4.  **JSON Hardening:**\n    *   Edit `openclaw.json`: Ensure `env` contains `FLEET_GAMES=\"730,570,440,252490\"`.\n\n5.  **Output:**\n    *   Hot Reload Latency.\n    *   Audit Checklist (Pass/Fail).\n    *   News Summary.\n    *   Upgrade Proposals."}],"timestamp":1771161857546}}
